<figureCitation box="[288,349,561,582]" captionStart="Figs" captionStartId="3.[175,215,1710,1729]" captionTargetBox="[159,1166,1288,1687]" captionTargetId="figure-499@3.[151,1171,1288,1687]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="Figs. 5–7. Chrysobothris species, male genitalia. 5) C. sabae; 6) C. marskeae; 7) C. thoracica." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4893212" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4893212/files/figure.png" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">Fig. 6</figureCitation>
). 
