Descarpentries
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,638,303,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
<keyLead pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
3. Lateral margins of pronotum strongly arcuate, pronotum widest at midpoint; posterior margin of pronotum red or greenish, never blue; suture blue at most just behind scutellum, not distinctly and brightly blue to level of first discal macula. Hispaniola ....... 
<taxonomicName authority="Fisher" authorityName="Fisher" authorityYear="1925" box="[427,638,873,894]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Chrysobothris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="84" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hispaniolae">
