Fisher
</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,638,303,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
<keyLead pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
3.′ Lateral margins of pronotum weakly arcuate, pronotum widest in anterior third; posterior margin of pronotum blue; suture bright metallic blue behind scutellum to level of first discal macula. 
<collectingCountry box="[353,476,1016,1037]" name="Puerto Rico" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">Puerto Rico</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[489,634,1016,1037]" name="Virgin Islands" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">Virgin Islands</collectingCountry>
, Leeward Islands..........................................4
</keyLead>
</paragraph>
</keyStep>
<keyStep pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
<paragraph blockId="3.[151,638,303,1233]" pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
<keyLead pageId="3" pageNumber="84">
